 59200 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.</span></div><div style="background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;border-left:4px solid #2563eb;"><strong style="display:block;color:#2563eb;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:4px;">Penang</strong><span style="color:#475569;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.55;">Jalan Sungai Dua, 11700 Penang, Malaysia.</span></div></div></div><div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:18px 20px;margin:14px 0;"><h3 style="margin:0 0 14px;font-size:16px;color:#0f172a;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:700;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1e3a8a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="3 11 22 2 13 21 11 13 3 11"/></svg>How to Find Us &mdash; Kuala Lumpur</h3><ol style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;"><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">1</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Enter <strong>KL Gateway Mall</strong> and go to <strong>Level G</strong>. You will see <strong>H&amp;M</strong> in the centre.</span></li><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">2</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Beside H&amp;M, look for the shop <strong>New Market</strong>. The small alley next to it leads to the bookstore (flower stall &amp; escalator on your left).</span></li><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">3</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Walk straight to the <strong>glass door</strong> beside the bookstore. Push through to <strong>KL Gateway Corporate Office Suite</strong>, then take the <strong>second glass door</strong>.</span></li><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">4</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Ring the bell &mdash; security will assist with registration. <strong>Please bring your identity card.</strong></span></li><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">5</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Tell the receptionist you are heading to <strong>G-3A-02 (Level 3A or 4)</strong>.</span></li><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">6</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Take the stairs beside the receptionist, follow signs to <strong>Block G</strong>, walk through the parking lot, then turn <strong>left</strong> at the signboard.</span></li><li style="display:flex;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;"><span style="flex-shrink:0;width:30px;height:30px;background:#16a34a;color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;line-height:1;">7</span><span style="color:#334155;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.6;">Tap the <strong>access card</strong> on the door, take the lift, tap again, and arrive at <strong>Level 4</strong>. You&rsquo;re here!</span></li></ol></div><div style="background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 18px;margin:14px 0;"><strong style="display:block;color:#0f172a;font-size:11.5px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:6px;">Management &amp; Mailing Address</strong><span style="color:#475569;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.55;">Level 29, Tower A, Vertical Business Suite, Avenue 3, Bangsar South, No.8, Jalan Kerinchi, 59200 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.</span></div><div style="margin-top:14px;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;"><iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3983.9284892982587!2d101.66388549999999!3d3.1136222999999994!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31cc35a711122273%3A0x2fb7c29a7126ea4c!2sTertiary%20Courses%20Malaysia!5e0!3m2!1sen!2ssg!4v1749020606897!5m2!1sen!2ssg" width="100%" height="320" style="border:0;display:block;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe></div>' WHERE block_id = 36 AND identifier = 'contacts';
